          To configure the check so that it checks for type name that is used in
          'extends' and ends with 'Throwable':
        </p>
        <source>
&lt;module name="MutableException"&gt;
  &lt;property name="extendedClassNameFormat" value="^.*Throwable$"/&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
        </source>
